{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/projects/arpro","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"michaeldemar.co"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cc90a29e-cbfe-5490-8c1f-626b39afb6d2","excerpt":"An AR Android application to let you view the latest Best Buy product in your home, from the comfort of your pyjamas. Background This project was developed by…","html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 430px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/14dc0402428c0624a013c806a27ccdfd/40c27/award.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"My friends and I accepting our second place prize!\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/14dc0402428c0624a013c806a27ccdfd/40c27/award.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/14dc0402428c0624a013c806a27ccdfd/a80bd/award.jpg 148w,\n/static/14dc0402428c0624a013c806a27ccdfd/1c91a/award.jpg 295w,\n/static/14dc0402428c0624a013c806a27ccdfd/40c27/award.jpg 430w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">My friends and I accepting our second place prize!</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>An AR Android application to let you view the latest Best Buy product in your home, from the comfort of your pyjamas.</p>\n<h3>Background</h3>\n<p>This project was developed by Michael DeMarco and Liang Liu, and backed by a business model developed by Benji Li, Daniel Frydman, and Ophir Greif. It was built at BizHacks 2020, a business-oriented hackathon sponsored by Best Buy and hosted at UBC. My team and I developed a business solution for Best Buy, and took home the 2nd place prize out of over 50 teams.</p>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>The project allowed users to determine what product dimensions were right for them from the comfort of their own home. Not sure if a 60” or 62” TV is right for you? Use our app to increment sizes of a mock TV displayed right on your wall, courtesy of the latest AR technology, or do a side-by-side comparison, or even enter a custom amount of inches!</p>\n<p>Check it out below!</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 296px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/58069fb8954de9d716e4b864215bf0c4/0a040/large-tv.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 193.91891891891893%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Editing a large TV within the application\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/58069fb8954de9d716e4b864215bf0c4/0a040/large-tv.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/58069fb8954de9d716e4b864215bf0c4/a80bd/large-tv.jpg 148w,\n/static/58069fb8954de9d716e4b864215bf0c4/1c91a/large-tv.jpg 295w,\n/static/58069fb8954de9d716e4b864215bf0c4/0a040/large-tv.jpg 296w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 296px) 100vw, 296px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Editing a large TV within the application</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 310px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b62b8847d9c3d04265b815ab4ca11170/ea106/small-tv.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 185.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Viewing a small TV within the application\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b62b8847d9c3d04265b815ab4ca11170/ea106/small-tv.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b62b8847d9c3d04265b815ab4ca11170/a80bd/small-tv.jpg 148w,\n/static/b62b8847d9c3d04265b815ab4ca11170/1c91a/small-tv.jpg 295w,\n/static/b62b8847d9c3d04265b815ab4ca11170/ea106/small-tv.jpg 310w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 310px) 100vw, 310px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Viewing a small TV within the application</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 320px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0d353eb74e6acd31920abfe55a01acfd/cb69c/products.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 179.05405405405406%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Viewing a list of different TVs in the application\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0d353eb74e6acd31920abfe55a01acfd/cb69c/products.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0d353eb74e6acd31920abfe55a01acfd/a80bd/products.jpg 148w,\n/static/0d353eb74e6acd31920abfe55a01acfd/1c91a/products.jpg 295w,\n/static/0d353eb74e6acd31920abfe55a01acfd/cb69c/products.jpg 320w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Viewing a list of different TVs in the application</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3>How it’s made</h3>\n<p>This project was built using Java and ARCore.</p>\n<h3>Challenges</h3>\n<p>Getting the AR to work properly was quite tricky; we ran into a number of issues finding suitable 3D models.</p>\n<h3>Accomplishments</h3>\n<p>The app works really nicely, and it took home 2nd place! It’s an interesting, minimalist take on the idea of “visualize furniture in your living room” that Ikea made quite popular.</p>\n<h3>Future</h3>\n<p>We should probably clean up the UI.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Best Buy AR Pro","date":"February 01, 2020","description":"An AR Android application to let you view the latest Best Buy product in your home, from the comfort of your pyjamas."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/arpro/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/rapviz/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"RapViz","type":"projects","published":true}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/csv/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSV Upload Tool","type":"projects","published":true}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","4032141823"],"slicesMap":{}}